01:04:56,642 --> 01:04:59,852
and have hidden myself all my life.

781
01:05:06,986 --> 01:05:08,106
Tae-wan.

782
01:05:13,701 --> 01:05:16,541
I never thought I'd tell you like this.

783
01:05:18,873 --> 01:05:19,793
The truth is, I--

784
01:05:20,374 --> 01:05:21,384
I'm gay.

785
01:05:27,173 --> 01:05:28,803
<i>And I love you so much.</i>

786
01:05:48,235 --> 01:05:50,145
THANKS TO JANG HYUN-SUNG
FOR SPECIAL APPEARANCE

787
01:06:06,170 --> 01:06:08,170
Tae-wan. Do you have time later today?

788
01:06:08,255 --> 01:06:09,915
Do you think a second season is possible?

789
01:06:10,007 --> 01:06:10,837
You can't do that.

790
01:06:11,717 --> 01:06:13,297
Did you think
producing a TV show was a joke?

791
01:06:13,886 --> 01:06:15,136
How will you take responsibility?

792
01:06:16,180 --> 01:06:18,020
I'm not interested
in other people's private life.

793
01:06:18,099 --> 01:06:19,269
Private life?

794
01:06:19,850 --> 01:06:21,440
-I...
-That's enough.

795
01:06:21,519 --> 01:06:22,479
I think I've heard enough.

796
01:06:23,729 --> 01:06:26,649
A-jin and Tae-wan... It's all my fault.

797
01:06:26,732 --> 01:06:27,942
-Isn't that Park Jin-seong?
-Where?

798
01:06:28,025 --> 01:06:30,435
I love spending time with that person.

799
01:06:30,528 --> 01:06:32,198
I guess I fell in love at first sight.

800
01:06:32,738 --> 01:06:35,698
<i>I think as long as you don't give up,</i>

801
01:06:35,783 --> 01:06:38,333
<i>things will work out for you.</i>

802
